While I do agree that teachers are doing this, they should not.  Teachers are not surrogate parents and should not be, you don't have the facilities for this, there is no way you can give the proper attention to 30+ kids that is needed to teach the proper Morels/Values and for that matter who are you to judge what My Childs Values should be, this is my point entirely, what if I am a bigot and wish (God forbid (PLEASE DON'T think I am)) my children to learn this?  Yes In most Sane and educated people this way of thinking is wrong, but is it our job to pass our morels right or miss guided to the children, NO... You job is to show them the path to make there own judgment, to teach them the BASICS and to teach them the mechanics of life, reading, reading comprehension, writing, math and history. <br>
<br>
Let those who should be teaching the proper family morels do just that... Granted it's not getting done now, but it is not the job of the Average teacher to do this.  Although maybe if you teach in a Religion based PRIVATE school then maybe I can see that as part of your job.... kids need parents, they need parents to teach right from wrong, judgment. &amp; Respect; to name a few.  This is done by spending time with the child, showing mercy, being strict, using Discipline (which is no longer truly available to parents or teachers, Don't even think of a good old fashion Spanking any more, child services will be on you like flies on shit) and love.<br>
<br>
<br>
Now yes the school systems suck, too many kids for not enough teachers, Teachers make shit for money, while some thug (I mean Football, baseball, Boxing Star) makes millions!!  We as Americans have some serious shit coming down the line in the next few generations as more of the &quot;top 10%&quot; rules more of the bottom 90%, what I mean is only those with means will become successful, while living off the blood of the ones with out... the ones with means will become less and less, while the ones with out will still be with out, there will just be more of us.  Education (knowledge), can save us, Ignorance will doom us forever<br>
